## 事件: any

``
- `dialog` { Dialog } 对话框

- `action` { string (https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Data_structures#String_type) } 被点击的按钮, 可能的值为:
- `positive` 确定按钮
- `negative` 取消按钮
- `neutral` 中性按钮

