### sum(...numbers)

**`6.2.0`** **`xObject`** **`Overload 1/3`**

- **numbers** { ... (documentation.html#documentation_可变参数)number (dataTypes.html#datatypes_number)[] (documentation.html#documentation_可变参数) } - 待求和数字
- **returns** { number (dataTypes.html#datatypes_number) }

返回所有数字的加和结果.

```js
/* 整数求和. */
console.log(Mathx.sum(1, 2, 3)); // 6
console.log(Mathx.sum(9)); // 9

/* 浮点数求和. */
console.log(Mathx.sum(0.1, 0.1)); // 0.2
console.log(Mathx.sum(0.1, 0.2, 0.3)); // 0.6000000000000001

/* NaN 保持其传染性. */
console.log(Mathx.sum(7, 8, 9, NaN)); // NaN

/* 无参将返回 NaN. */
console.log(Mathx.sum()); // NaN

